The petitions, lodged by various individuals and organisations including Law Society of Kenya (LSK) and rights activist Okiya Omtatah, are also challenging Ms Mwenda's possible ascension to the office of the governor following the impeachment of Mr Mike Sonko. 

The acting CJ constituted the bench following an order by Justice Anthony Mrima for empanelment of a multi-judge bench. 



